---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { url } from '../config/site';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="Mackay Refrigeration & Air-Conditioning has been keeping commercial refrigeration and HVAC running across Mackay and North Queensland for over 25 years."
>

  <!-- ── Page layout header ── -->
  <div class="page-layout-header">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span class="pulse"></span>
      About us
    </div>
    <h1>Built on<br /><span class="cold">cold expertise</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      We've been keeping refrigeration and air conditioning running across Mackay
      and North Queensland for over 25 years. One crew. Full scope. No subcontractors.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Page body ── -->
  <div class="page-body">
    <div class="md-content">

      <p>
        Mackay Refrigeration Pty Ltd (trading as Mackay Refrigeration and Air-Conditioning)
        was established to fill a gap in the Mackay commercial market — a contractor who
        could handle the full scope of refrigeration and HVAC work under one roof, with
        properly licensed technicians and no hand-offs to other trades.
      </p>

      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>
        We design, supply, install, commission, and maintain commercial refrigeration
        and air conditioning systems. That means cold rooms, freezer rooms, display
        cabinets, beer reticulation, commercial split systems, ducted HVAC — from
        initial brief to ongoing service contract.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our technicians hold current Arctick licences for refrigerant handling and our
        business is licenced with the QBCC. All work is documented and compliant.
      </p>

      <h2>Where we operate</h2>
      <p>
        Our base is Mackay, and we regularly service Airlie Beach, Cannonvale, Bowen,
        and Moranbah. For the right project, we'll go further — give us a call and we
        can work out logistics.
      </p>

      <h3>Service area</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Mackay (all suburbs)</li>
        <li>Airlie Beach &amp; Cannonvale</li>
        <li>Bowen</li>
        <li>Moranbah</li>
        <li>North Queensland (on request)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Emergency response</h2>
      <p>
        Cold chain failures don't keep business hours. We provide 24/7 emergency response
        for existing clients and new customers across our service area. If your compressor
        goes down or you've got a refrigerant leak, call us directly on
        <a href="tel:0749531245">07 4953 1245</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Licences &amp; registrations</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Licence / Registration</th>
            <th>Number</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>QBCC Contractor Licence</td>
            <td>15026021</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Arctick (refrigerant handling)</td>
            <td>AU00021</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>ABN</td>
            <td>32 107 715 766</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <blockquote>
        "If it runs on refrigerant or moves air commercially, we can install it,
        service it, and keep it running."
      </blockquote>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        Ready to discuss a project or set up a service contract?
        <a href={url('/contact')}>Send us a message</a> or call <a href="tel:0749531245">07 4953 1245</a>
        during business hours (Mon–Thu 7:30–4:30, Fri 7:30–2:00).
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>

  <CTA />
  <Footer />
</Base>
